You must return a valid JSON object matching this schema:
{
  "checks": [
    {
      "id": "string (rubric id)",
      "satisfied": boolean,
      "reasoning": "string (brief explanation)"
    }
  ],
  "overall_reasoning": "string (summary)"
}

